                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>Join us on a typical day in the life of an AbbVie employee driving change around the clock. We tag along with Krystal Bruno, an associate director&amp;nbsp;on our global philanthropy team. She collaborates with nonprofit grant partners to ensure progress on their goals and helps further their missions –&amp;nbsp;applying the same passion and precision to her morning runs and homemade meals.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
